<p>We’d love to jump on a video call with you to better understand your ideas and requests! During this first call, we’ll dive into your vision and discuss all the key elements needed to create something truly extraordinary organization, music, artists, lighting, stage, and dancefloor. My approach is highly structured and meticulously planned, ensuring that every detail is handled with precision and care. It’s important that your partner joins us too, <b>and that you connect using a laptop.</b> I’ll be sharing some carefully curated videos to give you a glimpse of the magic we can create together, and they’re best experienced on a <b>larger screen.</b></p>

